               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar "Synaxarion" for the first half of the year (fols.
                     4ra-170ra)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 4ra-31rc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     32ra-55va)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 56ra-82vc)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     83ra-113vb)
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 114ra-146vb)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     147ra-170ra)
 The commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns 
                     
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
